点的降息。 政策制定者正在尝试在下一步行动中找到平衡。鲍威尔称：「过早或降息过多可能会逆转我们在通胀上看到的进展，最终可能需要更紧缩的政策才能将通胀回归到 2%。但是，过晚或降息过少可能会不适度地削弱经济活动和就业。」 鲍威尔还在周三的讲话中重申，美联储的货币政策制定在大选年不会带政治色彩。他指出，这一立场对于制定正确的货币政策至关重要。鲍威尔对通胀持续回落信心不足仍认为今年会降息 - 手机金融界"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-eafe9c3337c10d01ba6df9d52c809348_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "21 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/649491848"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIvIyW6Ke28tQREAMaCTEwNjYwOTI1NyDLse+vBjAAON4BQBtyCTY0OTQ5MTg0OHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1712304620.886370", "card_id": "Q_651450193", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 39}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "大家对「现在已经不是工藤新一在扮演柯南而是柯南在扮演工藤新一」这观点是怎么看的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-c47f08b6ce856c78bd88234d7d133175_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "19 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/651450193"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IvIyW6Ke28tQREAMaCTEwNzA0NDQ2MCC+jLOwBjAAOElAHHIJNjUxNDUwMTkzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1712304620.887032", "card_id": "Q_333864283", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 1181}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "那些上清华的人高中都怎么过来的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "我很想得到好的学习技巧方法"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-6c863e5918b6a1a27d2da653e3d7d539_1440w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "19 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/333864283"}}, "attached_info": "CkA